    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777320/extras/8a7c6342c340e66d1d2724746e15371e.avif?t=1728776692\" width=616 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MALWARE Rewritten</strong> is a retro-styled action platformer, brought to you in a bright neon finish.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>OBJECTIVE // DESTROY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are a virus sent into the cyberspace with a single primary objective: Destroy and corrupt anything that comes your way, and if possible, gather valuable data scattered around. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777320/extras/f3d68644baf08c0fe229246cff9587f6.poster.avif?t=1728776692\" width=616 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777320/extras/f3d68644baf08c0fe229246cff9587f6.webm?t=1728776692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777320/extras/f3d68644baf08c0fe229246cff9587f6.mp4?t=1728776692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With every stage, the levels get progressively more complex, challenging, and introduce new obstacles to block your way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777320/extras/3d464c3103230a526a0005bd49f5512d.poster.avif?t=1728776692\" width=616 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777320/extras/3d464c3103230a526a0005bd49f5512d.webm?t=1728776692\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777320/extras/3d464c3103230a526a0005bd49f5512d.mp4?t=1728776692\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777320/extras/e037c1fbf93b69aab4d5bc496f9e0b87.webp?t=1728776692\" width=616 height=12 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast-paced platforming action! Dash through various areas of the cyberspace, leaving destruction in your wake.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The system will not give up without a fight, face a variety of enemies and defeat powerful bosses that dare to stand in your way.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unlock new abilities and increase your strength with each defeated boss, quickly adapting to their strategies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collect hidden data around the levels, smaller ones unlocking alternate colors, with larger data playing a bigger role later on.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Retro-inspired neon aesthetic and classic platformer mechanics, bringing an arcade feel to your library.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1777320/extras/5a092523332a352cf501b95974c0ea9d.avif?t=1728776692\" width=616 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you be able to become the strongest virus?</strong></p>",
